description.narrative:
(Part of the Climate Change Programme) This activity is focused on amplifying the Pacific voice, enabling the Pacific to tell its story, and influencing global negotiations with greater impact. It may include:
  • COP attendance
  • UNSG Climate Summit
  • IMO negotiations
  • Pacific Pavilion at COP 
  • Wilton Park II 
  • Climate Action Pacific Partnership Meeting
  • Analytical support 
  • Annual technical dialogues 
  • GHG Inventories and ICTUs
  • Negotiator training 
  • Chapter Scientist IPCC Report
  • Film/Art
  • Ad Hoc Support
